name: Seed You Later
description:
==========Info============

You are a helicopter seed that is too

scared to jump! Talk to others around the

forest to relieve some stress. Make sure 

to complete all four mini games before 

jumping.

=======Controls ============

WASD, arrow keys for movement

E, Z to interact

=======Sources used ========

KingHarvestMusic - Dancing in the moonlight

trash kid - hellacious hilltops

https://www.kenney.nl/assets/music-jingles

https://github.com/mattmarch/ACVoicebox

======

Made in 48 hours by Kaylee Chan & Edward Han
